CLASS:: VoxSelector
SUMMARY:: live labelled selection from upstream VoxMulti output
CATEGORIES:: VoxBox>Patching
RELATED:: Classes/VoxNode, Classes/VoxMulti, Classes/VoxRouter

DESCRIPTION::
VoxSelector is created by the >>* operator. It resolves its upstream VoxMulti output each time out is requested and returns the Vox with the selected label. It does not follow Vox.source references.

EXAMPLES::

code::
~tenor = ~canonChain >>* \tenor;
::
